Asked if Sanchez will leave this summer even if he doesn't renew his contract.<br />
<br />
Wenger replied with &quot;No.&quot;

Wenger on 'big' signings:<br />
<br />
&quot;Was Rob Holding a big signing? When you buy a player for &pound;40m everyone is positive, when &pound;2m he can't be good.&quot;

Wenger on &Ouml;zil &amp; Alexis: &quot;Anyway, they are under contract for another season. They will stay &amp; hopefully we can extend their contracts&quot;<br />
<br />
 Wenger: &quot;We cannot weaken the club or the team unless we can find someone of the same calibre &amp; they absolutely want to leave&quot;
